data.description:
** Multiple offers received. Highest and best offers due by Sunday, January 28, 2024, by 1 PM.
**

Welcome to this well-cared for 1.5 story home with an open floor plan, neutral paint colors and flooring, a quaint backyard, featuring a charming deck and fire pit - perfect for cozy gatherings. There are 3 parking spaces in the back, plus a 10X8 shed for your storage needs. With easy access to downtown Mankato and main highways, you will not want to miss this one! Schedule your showing today.
